# Drum break era populate

To add more drum-break videos to the DB (Playwright only, no YouTube Data API quota):

- From repo root: `npm run populate:drum-break-era` (defaults to `--target=300`).
- Overrides: `npm run populate:drum-break-era -- --target=50` or `--dry-run --target=5`.

Implementation: [`scripts/populate-drum-break-era.ts`](scripts/populate-drum-break-era.ts) uses `searchWithQueryPaginated` with `mode: "drumBreakEra"` in [`lib/youtube.ts`](lib/youtube.ts).
